      <hedline>
        <hl1>Alone at the Top</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>S R McAvoy letter asks about Roger Lowenstein's whereabouts since writing August 27 profile of Sanford I Weill (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Has anyone actually seen Roger Lowenstein since his article on Sandy Weill hit the stands? Given Weill's track record for dismissing those who do not agree with him, I suggest that someone check on your writer.</p>
        <p>S.R. McAvoy  New York</p>
      </block>
